{"text_id":193721,"tokens":["The"," scenario"," of"," dropping"," a"," ball"," through"," a"," hypothetical"," pipe"," that"," extends"," from"," the"," North"," Pole"," to"," the"," South"," Pole"," is"," a"," fascinating"," thought"," experiment"," that"," del","ves"," into"," the"," realms"," of"," physics",","," particularly"," gravity",","," motion",","," and"," the"," Earth","'","s"," structure","."," If"," we"," assume"," that"," the"," pipe"," is"," friction","less"," and"," that"," the"," Earth"," is"," a"," perfect"," sphere"," with"," uniform"," density",","," the"," ball"," would"," undergo"," a"," series"," of"," interesting"," motions"," due"," to"," gravitational"," forces",".","\n\n","Initially",","," as"," the"," ball"," is"," dropped"," into"," the"," pipe",","," it"," would"," accelerate"," towards"," the"," center"," of"," the"," Earth"," due"," to"," gravity","."," The"," force"," of"," gravity"," would"," pull"," the"," ball"," towards"," the"," Earth","'","s"," core",","," causing"," it"," to"," gain"," speed","."," As"," the"," ball"," approaches"," the"," center"," of"," the"," Earth",","," its"," velocity"," would"," be"," at"," its"," maximum"," because"," the"," gravitational"," force"," is"," strongest"," when"," the"," ball"," is"," closer"," to"," the"," center",".","\n\n","However",","," once"," the"," ball"," passes"," the"," center"," of"," the"," Earth",","," the"," situation"," changes","."," The"," gravitational"," force"," would"," now"," act"," in"," the"," opposite"," direction",","," trying"," to"," pull"," the"," ball"," back"," towards"," the"," center","."," As"," a"," result",","," the"," ball"," would"," begin"," to"," deceler","ate","."," By"," the"," time"," it"," reaches"," the"," South"," Pole",","," its"," velocity"," would"," have"," decreased"," to"," zero",","," assuming"," no"," energy"," losses","."," This"," is"," because"," the"," gravitational"," potential"," energy"," it"," gained"," while"," falling"," tow